"ProgressionMusic" local parameter:
0: Bass and Layer 1: + Delay melody 2: + Drums 3: + Bass 4: + Delay melody 2 5: + Harsh Synth 6: - Harsh synth, Delay melody 2, Drums. + "Sections" parameter changes to Loop B in unity. 7: - Bass , + Delay melody subtle changes (vol, rev, pan) 8: + Bass, + Lead synth + Chords (vol inc) 9: Everything back in. (Drums, Delay Layer, Guitar Lead,)
(+ "Sections" parameter changes to Loop C in unity on this value when the player exit level 3.)
10: 11: 12:
*Value 10 - 12 are used more in the "Music 2 Cave" event.
"Sections" local parameter:
Changes to loop B when entering the small cave with "ProgressionMusic" on value 6. Here some new stems are added (Marimba delay, lead synth. Delay layer, Guitar Lead, Chords, chords guitar,Pad) that are faded in and out depending on the value of "ProgressionMusic"
In the Transition to Zone 2 The "Sections" parameter changes to Loop C with the "ProgressionMusic" Parameter still on value 9. (Changes time signature, melody and adds additional stems. (Piano, and changes stems on already existing tracks.
"ToBossArea"
Is only suppose to be activated after scene 4 once the player is on the way up from the lift and on the way to the boss zone. So there is no real transition from any loop in this event that is supposed to be used in the game.
